Package com.dumbdogdiner.stickyapi.bukkit.gui

Class GUI

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.dumbdogdiner.stickyapi.bukkit.gui.GUI
  • public class GUI
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents an inventory GUI. Item stacks can be placed at locations in the GUI, and can be assigned tags and callbacks. A single GUI can be shared by multiple players, as updates will appear for all players viewing the GUI.
